$().ready(function(){$.getJSON("LoadBrands",function(n){let t="";$("#BrandId").empty();t+="<option value='0'> ---all--- <\/option>";$.each(n,function(n,i){t+="<option value='"+i.value+"'>"+i.text+"<\/option>"});$("#BrandId").html(t)})});$("#BrandId").change(function(){$.getJSON("ChangeBrand",{id:$("#BrandId").val()},function(n){let t="";$("#CarModelId").empty();$.each(n,function(n,i){t+="<option value='"+i.value+"'>"+i.text+"<\/option>"});$("#CarModelId").html(t)})});